#T_SP=de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.ner.type.NamedEntity|identifier|value
#T_CH=de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.coref.type.CoreferenceLink|referenceRelation|referenceType
#Text=Gun says : " Now rise , Wu of the Hou - Ting Dynasty , King of all the Earth Lands and glorious defender of Ba Sing Se .
#Text=Woohoo ... " Spectator # 2 says : " Woohoo ... " Wu says : " Thank you , for that incredibly brief , but very moving ceremony .
#Text=I am touched by the love of my devoted countrymen , who have worked so hard to restore their beloved leader to the throne .
#Text=One of them deserves special attention .
#Text=Kuvira , rise !
#Text=For your service to the realm , I would like to present you with the Kyoshi Medal of Freedom , our nation 's highest honor , which was somehow not stolen , unlike the royal pinky rings .
#Text=" Kuvira says : " Thank you .
#Text=And if you do n't mind , I would like to say a few words .
#Text=" Wu says : " Why not ?

#Text=We 've got six hours to fill ... " Kuvira says : " Growing up in Zaofu , with Suyin Beifong , I learned that the idea of a royal family passing a title from one generation to the next was archaic , and that technology and innovation should be what drives a nation forward .
#Text=It was the pathetic rule of kings and queens that caused the Earth Kingdom to descend into such incredible disarray .
#Text=It 's taken me three years to get it back on track , and there is no way I will allow it to slip back into the dark ages .
#Text=I 'd like to make an announcement to the world : the Earth Kingdom is no more .
#Text=And from here on out , this man has no authority .
#Text=" Wu says : " Wait , what ?
#Text=But I just got the royal brooch !
#Text=" Kuvira says : " I have created a new Earth Empire , and I will continue to lead it into the future myself , bringing about a new era of prosperity for my people .
#Text=" Crowd says : " We love you , Kuvira !
#Text=All hail the Great Uniter !
#Text=" Kuvira says : " And let me assure my fellow leaders of one thing : Anyone who crosses our borders or stands in our way , will be crushed .
#Text=" Crowd says : " Thank you , Kuvira !
#Text=All hail the Great Uniter !
#Text=" Wu says : " Worst coronation ever .
#Text="
